{"tha-ap432:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap432:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap432:0.3":"10 Sonnakontarikattheraapadana ","tha-ap432:1.1":"“Manobhavaniyam buddham, ","tha-ap432:1.2":"attadantam samahitam; ","tha-ap432:1.3":"Iriyamanam brahmapathe, ","tha-ap432:1.4":"cittavupasame ratam. ","tha-ap432:2.1":"Nittinnaogham sambuddham, ","tha-ap432:2.2":"jhayim jhanaratam munim; ","tha-ap432:2.3":"Upatittham samapannam, ","tha-ap432:2.4":"indivaradalappabham. ","tha-ap432:3.1":"Alabunodakam gayha, ","tha-ap432:3.2":"buddhasettham upagamim; ","tha-ap432:3.3":"Buddhassa pade dhovitva, ","tha-ap432:3.4":"alabukamadasaham. ","tha-ap432:4.1":"Anapesi ca sambuddho, ","tha-ap432:4.2":"padumuttaranamako; ","tha-ap432:4.3":"‘Imina dakamahatva, ","tha-ap432:4.4":"padamule thapehi me’. ","tha-ap432:5.1":"Sadhutiham patissutva, ","tha-ap432:5.2":"satthugaravataya ca; ","tha-ap432:5.3":"Dakam alabunahatva, ","tha-ap432:5.4":"buddhasettham upagamim. ","tha-ap432:6.1":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap432:6.2":"cittam nibbapayam mama; ","tha-ap432:6.3":"‘Iminalabudanena, ","tha-ap432:6.4":"sankappo te samijjhatu’. ","tha-ap432:7.1":"Pannarasesu kappesu, ","tha-ap432:7.2":"devaloke ramim aham; ","tha-ap432:7.3":"Timsatikkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap432:7.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham. ","tha-ap432:8.1":"Diva va yadi va rattim, ","tha-ap432:8.2":"cankamantassa titthato; ","tha-ap432:8.3":"Sovannam kontaram gayha, ","tha-ap432:8.4":"titthate purato mama. ","tha-ap432:9.1":"Buddhassa datvanalabum, ","tha-ap432:9.2":"labhami sonnakontaram; ","tha-ap432:9.3":"Appakampi katam karam, ","tha-ap432:9.4":"vipulam hoti tadisu. ","tha-ap432:10.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap432:10.2":"yamlabumadadim tada; ","tha-ap432:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap432:10.4":"alabussa idam phalam. ","tha-ap432:11.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap432:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap432:11.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap432:12.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap432:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap432:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap432:13.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap432:13.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap432:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap432:14.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sonnakontariko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap432:15.1":"Sonnakontarikattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap432:16.1":"Sakimsammajjakavaggo tecattalisamo. ","tha-ap432:17.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap432:18.1":"Sakimsammajjako thero, ","tha-ap432:18.2":"ekadussi ekasani; ","tha-ap432:18.3":"Kadambakorandakado, ","tha-ap432:18.4":"ghatassavanikopi ca. ","tha-ap432:19.1":"Sucintiko kinkaniko, ","tha-ap432:19.2":"sonnakontarikopi ca; ","tha-ap432:19.3":"Ekagathasatancettha, ","tha-ap432:19.4":"ekasattatimeva ca. "}